Provides classes for applying the old IMCCE theories VSOP87, Series96, and ELP2000 Lunar Solution.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Elp2000
    This class implements the Lunar Solution ELP2000 from the IMCCE.
    Elp2000_data1
    All the static data of the ELP2000 theory (part 1), in a separate file for managability.
    Elp2000_data2
    All the static data of the ELP2000 theory (part 2), in a separate file for managability.
    Series96
    A class to calculate planetary orbits based on the IMCCE's Series96.
    Vsop
    This class provides VSOP planetary positions for Mercury through Neptune.

Package jparsec.ephem.planets.imcce Description

Provides classes for applying the old IMCCE theories VSOP87, Series96, and ELP2000 Lunar Solution.

This package contains an implementation of the old theories VSOP87, Series96, and of ELP2000 Lunar Solution by the IMCCE. Series96 and VSOP require external .jar files in the classpath to be used, but Elp2000 data in included in this package.
